law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 5, effective July 1, 1960. -- Amended 1956 (2nd Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 5, sec. 4, effective March 28, 1956. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 63, sec. 4.
